00:58:04.070 --> 00:58:07.930
elevated. But in the setting of a preventative surgery, the

962
00:58:07.970 --> 00:58:11.650
things to highlight to patients are that, yes, this may definitely reduce the

963
00:58:11.710 --> 00:58:15.620
need for and/or the potential extent of screening and definitely reduces

964
00:58:15.670 --> 00:58:19.390
cancer risk. But of course, this is an irreversible surgery that can be

965
00:58:19.450 --> 00:58:23.150
associated with risks. And so these are a lot of the points that we

